claim.claim-text:
1. A magnetic shield comprising: 
a lid having a first layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface, and a second layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface; 
a base having a first layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface, and a second layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface; 
wherein the first layer of the lid is aligned with the first layer of the base when the shield is in use.

13. A magnetic shield comprising: 
a lid having a first layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface, and a second layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface; 
a base having a first layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface, and a second layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface; 
wherein the second layer of the lid is aligned with the second layer of the base when the shield is in use.

25. A magnetic shield comprising: 
a lid having a first layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface, and a second layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface; 
a base having a first layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface, and a second layer, having an inner surface and an outer surface; 
wherein the first layer of the lid is aligned with the first layer of the base and the second layer of the lid is aligned with the second layer of the base when the shield is in use.
